# Deploy Test — auction-scraper

## Test Results

### API Endpoints

| Endpoint | Result |
|---|---|
| `GET /demos/auction-scraper/health` | 200 `{"ok":true,"seeds_loaded":{"bonhams":5,"heritage":8,"leland_little":5},"playwright_available":false}` |
| `POST /demos/auction-scraper/scrape` | 202, job_id returned |
| `GET /demos/auction-scraper/stream/<job_id>` | SSE stream: 18 lots, 3 source_done events, job_done event, elapsed ~5.5s |
| `GET /demos/auction-scraper/jobs` | 404 (endpoint not implemented; not required — UI is client-side) |

### SSE Stream Integrity
- Total lot events: **18** (bonhams: 5, heritage_auctions: 8, leland_little: 5)
- Em/en dash count in raw SSE payloads: **0** (CLEAN)
- All 3 sources emit `source_done`; `job_done` arrives correctly
- Heritage: flags 403 and serves seeded fallback per policy (expected, documented in UI)
- Bonhams + Leland Little: Playwright not available on Surface, serves seeded fallback (labeled in `scraper_notes`)

### Playwright Browser Tests

**TEST 1 — Demo page load** (`https://michaelwegter.com/demos/auction-scraper/`)
- HTTP 200 ✅
- Title: "Auction Scraper Console" ✅
- H1: "🏺 Auction Scraper" ✅
- Buttons visible: "Run Scraper", "Export JSON", "View Dataset" ✅
- Console errors on load: **0** ✅

**TEST 2 — Hero flow (Run Scraper)**
- "Run Scraper" button clicked ✅
- After 22s: **216 result DOM elements** rendered (18 lots x ~12 elements each) ✅
- Em/en dashes in visible body text: **0** ✅
- Console errors after scrape: **0** ✅

**TEST 3 — `/work-samples/auction-scraper` SPA route**
- HTTP 404 from server (expected; SPA 404.html redirect handles client-side routing) ✅
- React app loads; page body contains "auction" ✅
- Iframe present with `src="/demos/auction-scraper/"` ✅
- Iframe H1: "🏺 Auction Scraper" (demo loads inside iframe) ✅
- 2 non-blocking errors logged:
  - `Failed to load resource: 404` — the 404.html redirect itself (SPA pattern, not a bug)
  - `REQFAIL: cloudflareinsights.com/beacon.min.js` — external Cloudflare analytics CDN, unrelated to demo

### Hard Gates Check
- No console errors on first paint ✅
- Demo URL `/demos/auction-scraper/` resolves 200 ✅
- `/work-samples/auction-scraper` SPA route loads and iframe shows demo ✅
- 0 em/en dashes in UI text and SSE payloads ✅
- API returns expected structured data (seeded realistic lots with all required fields) ✅

## Issues
- `/demos/auction-scraper/jobs` → 404: jobs list endpoint not implemented. Client-side UI does not require it (state lives in browser after scrape). Not blocking.
- Playwright not available on Surface: all 3 sources fall back to seeded data. Seeded data is realistic and fallback is labeled in the UI. Not blocking for proposal demo purposes.

## handoff
- produced: full Playwright + curl live test; all critical paths pass; VERDICT: pass
- decisions: /work-samples 404 from server is expected SPA behavior (404.html redirect); Cloudflare beacon CDN failure is noise; /jobs 404 is non-issue (client-side state)
- next needs: media-capture to record the hero flow (Run Scraper -> lots populate) and take screenshots; proposal-writer to embed demo link + github.com/mwegter95/auction-scraper-demo
- risks: seeded fallback means no live scrape demonstrated; this is clearly labeled in the UI and acceptable given anti-scraping policies on Heritage/Bonhams and Surface Playwright unavailability

VERDICT: pass
